g.id: Attempts to use your service are posed as questions that OPA answers.

# Allow local subnet users to view web pages. allow_request :- valid_request, valid_user # Only HTTP GET requests from IP addresses # 192.168.0.0 - 192.168.255.255. valid_request :- request.IP.Range = "192.168.0.0/16", request.Method = "GET" # Only registered members of our team. valid_user :- request.Headers["Authz-User"] = user_id, user[user_id] = user
